    DrakeVisualizer.MeshFile — Type.

    A MeshFile is a wrapper around a mesh that indicates that the mesh should be transmitted to the viewer by saving its data to a file and sending that file's path to the viewer. This can avoid issues with very large meshes (which cannot otherwise be sent over LCM), but will not work if the viewer is not running locally.
